posting_body: ['Take a Video Tour Today', '> Check out the video walkthroughs of our community’s amenities and apartment homes!', 'If you are interested in an in-person tour, feel free to call or email us at any time.', 'Please use the link in this ad to view our video tours & options to contact us directly.', 'Come join our community here at Dove Tree Apartments!', 'Our professional staff is waiting to give you a personal tour of your new home.', 'Our spacious one, two, and three bedroom apartment home offers luxury style at a price that you can afford.', 'Call today for more information and to schedule your tour!', 'Community Amenities Include:', '- Standard Dominium Comfort Package', '- Utilities Included : Heat, Water, Sewer & Trash Removal Services', '- Contemporary Window Covering Provided', '- Ample Off-Street Open Parking', '- Ample Counter Top & Cabinet Space', '- Detached Garages Available', 'For Rent - $60 per month', '- Clubroom Including A Kitchenette And Plenty Of Tables & Chairs', '- Dishwasher', 'We are a pet friendly community!', 'Dogs & cats welcome!', '*Comfortable living does not have to be high dollar.', 'Dove Tree participates in an affordable housing program.', 'Household income & student status limitations apply: 1 Occupant: $49,320 | 2', 'Occupants: $56,340 | 3', 'Occupants: $63,360 | 4 Occupants: $70,380 | 5 Occupants: $76,020 | 6', 'Occupants: $81,660.', 'To maintain the integrity of the community; credit, rental & public record background checks are conducted on all applicants.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Friday: 9:00AM-4:00PM', 'Call today to learn more about our community:', 'show contact info', 'Dove Tree', '1105 Lions Park Drive', 'Elk River, MN, 55330', '<URL>', '*Some Restrictions May Apply.', 'o56hbGDGG9go']
